last_episode_to_air.name: Just Mist
last_episode_to_air.overview: The kids take a field trip to a cloud forest and learn that clouds have water in them; the kids learn how crayons are made.

name: Elinor Wonders Why
overview: The adventures of an observant and curious bunny rabbit named Elinor and her friends Ari, a bat, and Olive, an elephant.

episodes.name: Hiding in Plain Sight
episodes.overview: Elinor and her pals are playing Hide and Go-Seek, but they are always spotted by the Goat twins! They observe camouflaged animals, and figure out to stay hidden, they need to camouflage themselves.

episodes.name: Owl Girl
episodes.overview: Elinor can't figure out what to be for Costume Day, and wants to find out why an owl has been sleeping all morning. After exploring at night with her mom, she figures out what she wants to be for Costume Day: an owl!

episodes.name: Backyard Soup
episodes.overview: Elinor is visiting her Baba and Bibi in Desert Town, and wants to make Backyard Soup! But, she can't find the ingredients! She figures out that certain plants grow in certain places.

episodes.name: Colorful and Tasty
episodes.overview: Elinor, Olive, and Ari have made carrot cupcakes, but they aren't selling in the park! Everyone loves cupcakes, but what's wrong? They figure out that they need to spread the color, and the smell!

episodes.name: The Amazing Expandable Clubhouse
episodes.overview: Elinor, Ari, and Olive have new members for their club, but there's not enough room for everyone in the clubhouse! They look for help from their snail friends, Norma and Lulu. They figure out that they can expand the clubhouse.

episodes.name: The Town Picnic
episodes.overview: Animal Town is having its Town Picnic, and Ari is getting impatient of waiting for Ms. Llama's ketchup. They find out that the ketchup is taking a long time to pour out of the bottle due to it being too goopy! They figure out that adding water can make things more runny!

episodes.name: The Science of Staying Warm
episodes.overview: Elinor, Olive and Ari get ready to go out and play in the snow.

episodes.name: The Tomato Drop
episodes.overview: Animal Town is having its Tomato Festival, and Elinor, Ari, and Olive are participating in the Tomato Drop! But, they can't keep the tomato from smushing! They figure out that they can use something as a chute to keep the tomato from smushing.

episodes.name: Look What I Can Do
episodes.overview: The kids are learning how to play soccer, but Elinor and Ari aren't as good as the others. Elinor can't kick the ball as far, and Ari keeps catching the ball with his hands! They figure out that everybody has their own special ability.

episodes.name: Burrowing Owl Girl
episodes.overview: Elinor is spending the day with her Bibi, and she fins an owl that doesn't act like a normal owl. She and Bibi notices that things look different, but they're still the same thing. She figures out that it was a burrowing owl she saw, and that she doesn't know everything about owls.

episodes.name: Olive's Tree
episodes.overview: Olive loves her special tree in the park. When it falls down, she is really sad. She and her friends figure out that the tree will still have a role in the park as a wildlife tree.

episodes.name: To Bee or Not to Bee
A Change of Art
episodes.overview: Elinor, Olive, and Ari are at art class with Mr. Lion, but they're out of paint! They find that grass and berries can make paint-like items. They figure out that you can use things from nature to make art.

episodes.name: Litterbug
episodes.overview: There's litter in the park, and the kids want to help Mrs. Hippo get rid of the litter. But, there's even more around the town! Elinor figures out that the cause of the litter is her, Olive, Ari, and Mrs. Hippo.

episodes.name: The Violin Lesson
episodes.overview: Crickets inspire Olive to play her violin; while flying in a hot air balloon, Elinor and her friends learn why birds fly high.

episodes.name: Clean Captain
episodes.overview: Elinor is the new Clean Captain at school and takes things too far; Ari has a loose tooth.

episodes.name: Just Mist
episodes.overview: The kids take a field trip to a cloud forest and learn that clouds have water in them; the kids learn how crayons are made.
